WHAT IS IT?
-----------

  'Bloksters' is a Workbench game in which you send blocks from
the border to a 9 by 9 spaces 'arena', so they make line-ups of 4
or more blocks of the same colour. When blocks of the same colour
are next to each other, they get 'connected' by a small link.

  As you may have guessed, there is a catch: whenever a block is
sent and does not complete a line-up of at least 4 blocks of the
same colour, a new block will appear randomly in the arena...
which may complicate matters a little...

  And as if it was not enough, in order to be able to send a block
in the arena, another block must be in line with the block you
want to send. Ohterwise, clicking on the border block will have no
effect.

  The game ends when the arena is full, or if it is impossible to
add a block in the arena, because all spaces next to the borders
are occupied.

  Have fun!

